title: hyundai trajet manual
description:
The program is in Adobe PDF format and is included on the disc, so there is nothing to download from the internet. Will work on any system that can currently read an Adobe Pdf
If you own a Trajet 1999 - 2008 then this is the ideal solution for you if need to know something about your car or if you have to make repairs.
Presented for you in electronic format you can just print out the page you need then dispose of it when you have completed your task.
This program covers the following;
Engine Mechanical
Engine Electrical
Emissions Control
Fuel System
Clutch System
Transaxle / Transmission
Driveshaft & Axle
Suspension System
Steering System
Brakes
Restraints
Body
Body Electrical
Heating, Ventilation, Air-Conditioning

Applicable engines are;
2.4l 4cyl. DOHC ( 2351cc )
2.7l V6 DOHC ( 2656cc )

This is an absolute must to save you money when your vehicle needs attention.
I think it also applies to Hyundai SANTA FE SONATA SOLARIS TERRACAN TUCSON VERACRUZ
